mily:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 회원재가입 승낙을 얻은 경우에는 예외로 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">7. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 귀책사유로 인해 이용계약이 해지됨으로써 발생한 손해는 당해 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>이 부담하여야 하며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 관련 법령에 규정이 없는 한 책임을 부담하지 않습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">제</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">10</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">조</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스 제공 및 중단</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span></b><br></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 특별한 사유가 없는 한 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>를 연중무휴<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, 1</span>일 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">24</span>시간 제공함을 원칙으로 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>다만<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 종류나 성질에 따라 제공하는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>중 일부에 대해서는 별도로 이용시간을 정할 수 있으며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>이 경우 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 그 이용시간을 사전에 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 공지 또는 통지하여야 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">2 “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 아래의 각 호에 의거하여 일시적으로 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">를 중단할 수 있습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">” </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">중단 시간과 작업 내용은 사전에 공지 또는 통지하며 최대한 빠른시간내에 서비스를 재개하도록 최선의 노력을 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">다만</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">가 사전에 공지 및 통지할 수 없는 부득이한 사유가 있는 경우 이러한 사정이 해소된 이후 즉시 통지합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="0"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">① </span>시스템 유지보수<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>장애를 해결하기 위한 각종 점검<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>시스템 업그레이드를 위한 교체작업이 필요한 경우</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">② </span>기간 통신사업자가 전기통신서비스 제공을 중지하는 경우</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">③ </span>천재지변<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>전쟁<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>폭동<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>테러<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>해킹<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, DDOS, </span>전력공급 중단 등의 불가항력적인 사유에 의해 서비스 제공이 객관적으로 불가능한 경우<span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="0"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">④ </span>기타 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>가 필요하다고 판단되는 경우</p><p class="0"><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">3. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 사업종목 전환<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>사업의 포기<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>업체간 통합<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>파산 또는 회생절차 개시 등 정상적인 영업활동이 곤란한 경우 또는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 영업상 필요한 경우 서비스 내용을 변경하거나 서비스를 종료할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>이 경우 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">3</span>조<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>약관의 명시 및 개정 등<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">) 3</span>항에서 정한 방법에 따라 서비스 내용의 변경사항 또는 종료를 공지 또는 통지할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><b>제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">11</span>조<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>자료내용의 책임과 회사의 정보 수정 권한<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span></b></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. </span>자료내용은 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>이 등록한 개인정보와 사이트에 게시한 게시물을 말하는 것으로서<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>모든 자료내용의 관리와 작성은 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>본인이 하는 것이 원칙이나 사정상 위탁 또는 대행관리를 하더라도 자료내용의 책임은 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 주기적으로 자신의 자료를 확인하여 항상 정확하게 관리가 되도록 노력해야 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">2. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 자료내용 및 게시물을 사실에 근거하여 성실하게 작성해야 하며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>만일 자료의 내용이 사실이 아니거나 부정확하게 작성되어 발생하는 모든 책임은 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 귀속됩니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">제</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">12</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">조</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">건설인 서비스 이용제한 등</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span></b><br></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 서비스의 안정성과 신뢰성을 위하여 아래 각 호의 사유가 발생하는 경우 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 서비스 이용을 정지하거나 이용계약을 해지할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="0"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">① </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 행위가 본 약관 제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">6</span>조<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>서비스 이용신청의 승낙과 제한<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">) 6</span>항의 금지행위에 해당하는 경우</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">② </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>자격이 정지되거나 상실되는 경우</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">③ </span>본 약관 또는 이용 정책 등을 위반한 경우 </p><p class="0"><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">2. </span>제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1</span>항의 이용제한 등은 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>가 정한 통지방법에 따라 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 그 의사를 표시한 때에 효력이 발생합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">3. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스 이용이 정지된 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 해당하는 기간에는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">건설인</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">” </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스를 이용할 수 없습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">4. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 서비스 이용제한에 해당하는 사유를 소명하였을 경우에 제한조치를 해제할 수 있습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">제 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">장 서비스 및 결제사항</span></b><br></p><p class="0"><br></p><p class="0"><b>제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">13</span>조<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>구인자의 지원하기<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span></b></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. </span>건설인 어플리케이션의 특징은 최초 구인업체에서 직종<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>성별<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>기술숙련도<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>작업시간<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>대금 등을 게시하면 스마트폰 어플리케이션을 통해 다수의 구직자에게 내용이 발송되고<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>이를 확인한 구직자가 자신에게 맞는 조건을 클릭하게 됩니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>구인업체는 응찰한 구직자 프로필 심사 후 구인업체에 적합한 구직자를 클릭<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>낙찰<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span>함으로써 계약이 성립하게 됩니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>장비관련 회원도 </p><p class="0">같습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">2. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">임금은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구인회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 사회통념에 따라 정하고</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구인회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구인회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 금액을 정확히 확인하고 지원하기를 해야 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">장비관련 회원도 같습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">제</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">14</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">조</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스 이용 시 주의사항</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span></b><br></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"></span>1. 계약확정 시 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>구인회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>구직회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 필요한 사항<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>임금<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>현장위치<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>작업소요 시간<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>준비물품 등<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span>을 알려줘야하며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>장비관련회원 역시 같습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">제</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">15</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">조</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스 이용 및 수수료</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span></b><br></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. “</span>회원가입<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 무료이며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 서비스 이용료를 부과할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">2. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 필요한 경우 서비스 이용료를 변경할 수 있으며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>변경사항은 공지사항을 통하여 공지합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">3. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 거래 활성화 등을 위하여 우수<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 서비스 이용료를 할인할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>또한 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 특정 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 서비스 이용료를 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>가 정하는 일정한 기준과 절차에 따라 조정 또는 면제할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><br></p><p class="0"><br></p><p class="0"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">제</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">16</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">조</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">충전금액입금 및 환불정책</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span></b><br></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 서비스 정책에 따라 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 직업정보제공 서비스를 이용할 수 있는 금액을 결재 해야 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">2. </span>시스템 오류로 차감된 금액은 오류로 차감된 금액만큼 충전해 드립니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">3. “</span>충전금액<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>환불요청 시 개인계좌 등의 수단으로 환불됩니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>단 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>가 무상으로 지급한 충전금액은 환불되지 않으며 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1</span>개월내 미사용시 자동소멸됩니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">6. </span>사용에 관한 상세한 사항은 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>가 정한 정책에 따르며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 건설인 화면을 통하여 이를 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 안내합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><br></p><p class="0"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">제 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;">4</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">장 의무관련 사항</span></b></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span><br></p><p class="0"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><b>제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">19</span>조<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 의무<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span></b></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 관계법령과 본 약관이 금지하거나 미풍양속에 반하는 행위를 하지 않으며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>지속적<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>안정적으로 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>를 제공하기 위하여 최선의 노력을 기울입니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">2. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>이 안전하게 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>를 이용할 수 있도록 이용자의 개인정보<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>신용정보 포함<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span>보호를 위한 보안시스템을 갖추어야 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">3. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 회원가입 시 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 자세한 개인정보를 강요하지 않습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>다만 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>스스로 자신의 신뢰도를 향상하기 위하여 자발적인 정보입력을 위한 기능을 제공합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">4. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 정기적으로 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 당사의 서비스 내용 및 이용 안내에 대한 정기적인 서신을 보낼 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.(</span>통지<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, SMS, E-mail, </span>어플리케이션 알림 등<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">5. “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>으로부터 제기된 의견이나 불만이 정당하다고 인정할 경우에는 이를 즉시 처리하여야 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>그 처리과정 및 결과에 대해서는 공지사항을 활용하거나 연락처 및 이메일 등을 통하여 통보 및 통지합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">6. </span>천재지변 등 예측하지 못한 일이 발생하거나 시스템의 장애가 발생하여 서비스가 중단될 경우 이에 대한 손해에 대해서는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>가 책임을 지지 않습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>다만 자료의 복구나 정상적인 서비스 지원이 되도록 최선을 다할 의무를 집니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">7. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 자료를 본 서비스 이외의 목적으로 제 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">3</span>자에게 제공하거나 열람시킬 경우 반드시 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 동의를 얻어 게시합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">8. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>이 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>사이트<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에 등록한 정보<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>구인<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">․</span>구직공고 내용은 사이트를 방문하는 일반 대중에게 공개함을 원칙으로 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">9. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>이 결제 시<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, “</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 그 여부를 확인할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>또한 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>결제수단의 적법성 등에 대한 확인이 완료될 때까지 임의로 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>이용중지를 할 수 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">10. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 분쟁이 발생한 경우 분쟁해결을 위하여 성실히 임하여야 하며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>분쟁해결 시 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 불성실로 인하여 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에 손해가 발생한 경우 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 이에 대한 책임을 부담하여야 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span><br></p><p class="0"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><b>제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">20</span>조<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>회원의 의무<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span></b></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">1. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>상호간 등록<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">/</span>신청<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">/</span>선택 전에 반드시 상세내용과 거래의 조건을 정확하게  확인한 후 충분한 검증을 통해 거래를 확정해야 합니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>거래내용과 거래조건을 확인하지 않고 거래를 진행하여 발생한 모든 손실 및 손해는 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에게 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">2. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 약관 및 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">와 관련하여 고지하는 내용을 준수하여야 하며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">약관 및 고지 내용을 위반하거나 이행하지 아니하여 발생하는 모든 손실</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">손해에 대하여 책임을 부담합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">3. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 구인</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;">․</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구직 및 장비관련에 관하여 신청하고자 할 때는 회사에서 정한 방법에 의거 결재금액을 사전구매하여야 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">4. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 결제 수단으로 전자결제나 무통장입금 등의 어플리케이션 전자결제시스템 등을 사용할 경우 비밀번호 등 정보유실방지는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">” </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">스스로 관리해야 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">단</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">사이트</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 결함에 따른 정보유실 발생에 대한 책임은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의무에 해당하지 아니합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">5. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구인회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">과 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구직회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">간 거래내용과 거래조건에 대하여 어떠한 보증이나 책임도 부담하지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">장비관련 회원도 같습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">따라서 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 거래확정 시 스스로의 책임하에 거래를 진행하여야 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">6. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 회원개인정보에 대한 보증을 하지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">또한 작업수행 중 발생한 문제의 책임은 전적으로 계약을 맺은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">당사자에게 귀속되기에 신중히 검토한 후 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">를 이용해야 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">7. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 유료서비스 결제방법을 사용함에 있어 반드시 본인 명의의 결제수단을 사용하여야 하며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">타인의 결제수단의 임의사용 등을 하여서도 안됩니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">타인의 결제수단을 임의 사용함으로써 발생하는 손실과 손해에 대한 모든 책임은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">에게 있습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">8. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 입력한 정보는 진실하여야 하며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">만일 허위 기타 부정한 정보를 입력하여 다른 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">에게 피해가 발생할 경우 그에 대한 민</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;">․</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">형사상의 책임을 포함한 일체의 책임은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">본인에게 귀속됩니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">9. ‟</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">가 유료서비스를 안전하게 제공할 수 있도록 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">에 협조하여야 하며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">가 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 이 약관위반 행위를 발견하여 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">에게 해당 위반행위에 대하여 소명을 요청할 경우 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">요청에 적극 응하여야 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">10. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 관계법령과 본 약관의 규정 및 기타 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">가 공지 및 통지하는 사항을 준수하여야 하며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">기타 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 업무에 방해되는 행위를 해서는 안됩니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">11. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 본 약관 및 고지하는 내용을 준수하여야 하며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이를 위반하거나 이행하지 아니하여 발생하는 모든 손실</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">손해에 대하여 책임을 부담해야 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">12. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>은 본 서비스를 건전한 목적으로 사용해야 하며 이용중 다음 각 호의 행위를 해서는 안됩니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span></p><p class="0">  <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->  <o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">① </span>다른 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 회원정보를 도용하거나 부정하게 취득<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>사용하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">② </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에 대하여 허위사실을 유포하거나 업무방해를 하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">③ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>에 해킹 또는 바이러스 유포<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, D-DDOS</span>공격 등의 공격으로 정상적인 운영을 어렵게 하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">④ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>지적재산권 등의 권리를 침해하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">⑤ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">” </span>명예훼손 및 모욕하는 행위를 하거나 비방하는 내용을 작성하여 유포하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">⑥ </span>스팸<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>광고성 정보 등 일정한 내용을 계속적으로 전송하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">⑦ </span>서비스의 안정적인 운영에 지장을 주거나 줄 우려가 있다고 판단되는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">⑧ </span>사이트의 정보 및 서비스를 이용한 영리 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">⑨ </span>신체적 상해를 가하거나 언어적 폭력 등으로 피해를 끼친 경우</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">⑩ </span>범죄행위를 목적으로 하거나 기타 범죄행위와 관련된 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"> </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">⑪ </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>서비스<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>를 이용하여 얻은 정보를 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>의 사전동의 없이 복사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>복제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>번역<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>출판<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>방송 기타의 방법으로 사용하거나 이를 타인에게 제공하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"></span>⑫ 건설인이 제공하는 프로필 및 개인정보<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>키워드<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>사진<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>이름<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>연락처 등<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span>등을 무단복사<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>저장<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span>하거나 이를 유출하여 외부에 게시하는 행위</p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;"></span>⑬ 기타 그 밖에 선량한 풍속<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>사회질서에 위배되거나 관계법령에 위반하는 행위 </p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">12. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 권한은 타인에게 양도 및 판매가 불가능합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">13. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">에서 허용한 정당한 거래</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구직회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 최종선택과 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">구인회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 수락을 통해 매칭이 성사된 경우</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">를 통해 상대방의 연락처를 얻는 것이 아닌 건설인 키워드</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">나의 프로필</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">사진</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">댓글</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">일감 내용 등</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 작성할 수 있는 서비스 내의 모든 영역에 일체의 개인연락처</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이메일</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">전화번호</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">등을 기재하거나 이를 유도하여</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">부당하게 연락수단을 공개하면 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">를 부정하게 이용하는 행위로 간주하여 강제해지 처리될 수 있으며 이로 인한 손해에 대해 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 책임지지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">14. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">은 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">사이트</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">를 통해 열람한 정보를 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">” </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">및 당사자의 허락없이 재배포 할 수 없으며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">본인정보에 대한 캡처</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">출력 및 복사 등의 관리책임은 전적으로 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">” </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">당사자에게 있습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">15. </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">본 약관을 위반하거나 기타 대한민국 관계법령에 위반하는 행위에 대해서는 경고없이 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 권한이 박탈되며 이에 대해 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">에게 어떠한 보상도 하지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span><br></p><p class="0"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="0"><b>제<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">21</span>조<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">(</span>개인정보보호<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">)</span></b></p><p cla