t-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">․</span>제공할 뿐이며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>당사자를 대리하지 않습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. “</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>간 제공한 정보 및 그 정보의 진실성 또는 적법성 등 일체에 대하여 보증하지 않으며<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">, </span>그와 관련하여 어떠한 책임도 부담하지 않습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">. </span>그러므로 <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">“</span>회원<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">”</span>간 성립된 거래와 제공한 정보에 대한 책임은 계약 당사자에게 있습니다<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.0pt;mso-text-raise:0.0pt;">.</span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">2. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 귀책사유로 인한 서비스이용 장애에 대하여는 책임을 지지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">3. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">” </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">화면에서 링크</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">배너 등을 통하여 연결된 제 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">자와 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">” </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">간에 이루어진 거래에 대해서 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 개입하지 않으며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">해당 거래에 어떠한 책임도 부담하지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">4. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 자신의 개인정보 및 계정</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">(ID, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">로그인 비밀번호</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">등을 타인에게 제공하거나 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 관리소홀로 유출됨으로써 발생하는 피해에 대해서 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 책임을 부담하지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">5. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">서비스</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이용과 직접적으로 관련이 없는 분쟁에 관여하지 않으며</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">간 또는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">과 제 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">자간의 분쟁을 포함하여 도난</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">폭행 등의 각종 범죄 등에 대해서는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">건설인</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">의 과실이 없는 한 책임을 부담하지 않습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span><br></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><br></span></p><p class="0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">6. “</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회사</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">는 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">“</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">회원</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">”</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">이 게재한 정보</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">자료</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter